column5: Ixoreal Biomed's award-winning KSM-66 is the highest-concentration, highly bio-available full-spectrum root extract of ashwagandha, the most revered botanical from Ayurveda. Now in about 650 products, it is the best-selling ashwagandha root extract today. Extensive clinical evidence via 24 human studies shows KSM-66 to be effective in reducing stress, anxiety, improving natural testosterone production, cardiorespiratory endurance, muscle strength, muscle size, muscle recovery, attention and focus.   Our science team likes to call KSM-66 the "World's Best Ashwagandha", for five reasons: (1) KSM-66 has highest concentration of all major full-spectrum root extracts available on the market today. In a recent study it was found to have higher bioavailability. (2) KSM-66 has the most extensive set of research studies and clinical trials.  (3) We are the only major branded  ashwagandha maker in the world that owns and controls the entire supply chain. We have own farms, labs, manufacturing and distribution. Because of the tight vertical integration, we are able to ensure excellent quality and pricing. (4) KSM-66 has a neutral taste, unlike other Ashwagandha extracts that are rather bitter to taste, making it an excellent choice for food and beverage manufacturers. (5) KSM-66 is the botanical with the highest number of quality certifications, including labels of Organic, Non-GMO, Gluten Free, Kosher, ISO's and of GMP from USP, NSF, WHO, UL-NPA.
